summary: An Ordinance setting aside and transferring to the control and jurisdiction of the Board of Park Commissioners Lots One (1), two (2), three (3), four (4), eight (8), nine (9), ten (10), eleven (11) and twelve (12), in Block 42 D. T. Denny's Home Addition to the City of Seattle. for Park and playground purposes, in consideration of a payment from the City Park Fund into the General Fund of the sum of Thirty Thousand ($30,000.00) Dollars.
